inquiries.query:
/*
In the invoices_fact tables subtract the hours rate from the hours spent to estimate 
the remaining budget allocation if hours_rate represents a fixed cost per hour. 
Return the
*/

SELECT 
    activity_id,
    hours_spent,
    hours_rate,
    hours_spent - hours_rate AS remaining_budget_estimate
FROM 
    invoices_fact;
